sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Next.js UI
    participant PS as ProviderSelect
    participant MS as ModeSelect
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Agent as Agent Orchestrator

    User->>UI: Open page
    UI->>API: GET /providers
    API-->>UI: {providers:[gemini,claude,groq],<br/>modes:[react,native],<br/>default_provider:"gemini",<br/>default_mode:"react"}
    UI->>PS: render dropdown<br/>(default: gemini)
    UI->>MS: render dropdown<br/>(default: react)

    rect rgb(15, 53, 40)
    Note over User,MS: Scenario A — default Gemini + ReAct
    User->>UI: drop PDF (no dropdown change)
    UI->>API: POST /analyze<br/>file + provider=gemini + mode=react
    API->>Agent: run_agent(text, "gemini", "react")
    Note over Agent: dispatches to _run_react_loop
    Agent-->>API: result
    API-->>UI: JSON + metadata{<br/>model:"gemini-2.5-flash",<br/>mode:"react"}
    end

    rect rgb(42, 26, 74)
    Note over User,Agent: Scenario B — switch to Claude + Native
    User->>PS: select "Claude"
    PS->>UI: setProvider("claude")
    Note over MS: "native" option<br/>now enabled
    User->>MS: select "Native tool-use"
    MS->>UI: setMode("native")
    User->>UI: drop PDF
    UI->>API: POST /analyze<br/>file + provider=claude + mode=native
    API->>Agent: run_agent(text, "claude", "native")
    Note over Agent: dispatches to<br/>_run_claude_native_agent
    Agent-->>API: result
    API-->>UI: JSON + metadata{<br/>model:"claude-sonnet-4-6",<br/>mode:"native"}
    end

    rect rgb(58, 31, 14)
    Note over User,Agent: Scenario C — switch provider, mode auto-resets
    User->>PS: select "Groq"<br/>(while mode=native)
    PS->>UI: setProvider("groq")
    UI->>MS: handleProviderChange detects<br/>non-Claude + native → resets mode
    MS->>UI: setMode("react")
    Note over MS: "native" option<br/>now disabled
    User->>UI: drop PDF
    UI->>API: POST /analyze<br/>file + provider=groq + mode=react
    API->>Agent: run_agent(text, "groq", "react")
    Note over Agent: dispatches to _run_react_loop<br/>(same code path as Scenario A)
    Agent-->>API: result
    API-->>UI: JSON + metadata{<br/>model:"llama-3.3-70b-versatile",<br/>mode:"react"}
    end
